config LIBDITHER
	bool "Image dithering library"
	help
	  Enable the libdither image dithering library. Provides algorithms
	  to convert 8-bit grayscale images to 1-bit monochrome, suitable
	  for use with monochrome displays such as OLED and e-ink panels.

	  Supported algorithms: Threshold, Ordered (Bayer 4x4), and
	  Floyd-Steinberg error diffusion.
